1. e4 e5 2. f4! { Players gonna play agressive, we opened f file, and get the centre, it also fun! } 2... exf4 3. Nf3 g5 { Protecting the pawn } 4. Bc4 g4 { Best move } 5. O-O!? { This is very aggressive muzio gambit. } 5... gxf3 6. d4! { Sacrifice another pawn } 6... fxg2? { Ooops... } 7. Bxf7+!! { Bro got depressed } 7... Kxf7 8. Qh5+! Ke7 9. Rxf4 Nf6 $7 { Protecting from checkmate } 10. Rxf6!! { Did I blundered??? } 10... Kxf6 11. Bg5+! { Seems like no, we get free queen } 11... Kg7 12. Bxd8 $16 { Works on 100-1200 elo! } *

